-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jxb1665702610180.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jxb1665702610180.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jxb1665702610180.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jxb1665702610180\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n    Print Header </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Print Header is a Frame in a Form or Report component that is used to print\n    information at the top of each printed page. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95819e1_d95820e1_d95821e1\">There can only be one Print Header in a component. It\n      typically contains variable information such as a date, page number, title and so on.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__section_rhf_xjs_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1002175e54\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__image_gk1_2ks_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/print_header.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">phe</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wza1665703030894.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wza1665703030894.html\" title=\"A Non-Database Entity is an Entity that has its Database Behavior property set to F. It can be used to model a group of controls, constant data, derived data, or non-persistent data that do not need to be stored in a database. It cannot be mapped to a database table.\">Non-Database Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eyt1681415255117.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eyt1681415255117.html\" title=\"An area is a development object that represents an area frame on a Form or Report component. It is used to group objects and style the area it encloses.\">Area</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gya1665702610097.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gya1665702610097.html\" title=\"A Frame is a Development Object that graphically represents a Development Object in the layout of a Form or Report component.\">Frame</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jxb1665702610180__table_d10634e1_d10635e1_d10636e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/phe:HEADER.USYS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__section_lcm_fks_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1002175e281\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95828e1_d95829e1_d95830e1\">Print Header specializes Frame in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__ul_nqc_hks_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38675e1_d38676e1_d38677e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95831e1_d95832e1_d95833e1\">Its can only have a Form or Report component as\n            parent object.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38678e1_d38679e1_d38680e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95834e1_d95835e1_d95836e1\">It has the fixed name\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">HEADER.USYS</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38681e1_d38682e1_d38683e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95837e1_d95838e1_d95839e1\">It cannot contain database entities.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38684e1_d38685e1_d38686e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95840e1_d95841e1_d95842e1\">It can have a code container with a  getFocus trigger.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38687e1_d38688e1_d38689e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95843e1_d95844e1_d95845e1\">A Form or Report can have only one Print Header.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__section_i3k_hks_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1002175e328\">Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95849e1_d95850e1_d95851e1\">Object properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__ul_gzp_3ks_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38690e1_d38691e1_d38692e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38693e1_d38694e1_d38695e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38696e1_d38697e1_d38698e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95852e1_d95853e1_d95854e1\">Presentation properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__ul_nzp_3ks_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38699e1_d38700e1_d38701e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38702e1_d38703e1_d38704e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38705e1_d38706e1_d38707e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38708e1_d38709e1_d38710e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38711e1_d38712e1_d38713e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gmd1665702587249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gmd1665702587249.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a border is displayed around the area frame, entity or occurrence frame, or field. It is set from the context menu in the form canvas.\">Border</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38714e1_d38715e1_d38716e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__p_d95855e1_d95856e1_d95857e1\">Printing properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__ul_zzp_3ks_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38717e1_d38718e1_d38719e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rdh1665702703470.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rdh1665702703470.html\" title=\"Indicates whether printing is suppressed if there is no data available for this object. Valid values are True (default) or False.\">Do not print empty occurrence</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__section_qnd_lks_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1002175e459\">Triggers</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__ul_uwz_lks_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxb1665702610180__li_d38804e1_d38805e1_d38806e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"biv1665702630863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/biv1665702630863.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to the frame getting focus (usually when the frame is about to be printed).\">trigger getFocus (Frame)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ljw1665702610670.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Area Frames for Printing</a><p>In reports, area frames can be used to add and protect text as part of an entity in Report components.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614036\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614036\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Print Header Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Print Header A Print Header is a Frame in a Form or Report component that is used to print information at the top of each printed page. There can only be one Print Header in a component. It typically contains variable information such as a date, page number, title and so on. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: phe Main Development Object? No Part of: Component Contains: Property , Code Container , Non-Database Entity , Area Generalization: Frame Specializations: Compilation Output: — URI format: cpt: ComponentName /phe:HEADER.USYS Specialization Print Header specializes Frame in the following ways: Its can only have a Form or Report component as parent object. It has the fixed name HEADER.USYS . It cannot contain database entities. It can have a code container with a getFocus trigger. A Form or Report can have only one Print Header. Properties Object properties: Name Type Location Presentation properties: Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Border Index Color Printing properties: Do not print empty occurrence Triggers trigger getFocus (Frame) Related Links Area Frames for Printing In reports, area frames can be used to add and protect text as part of an entity in Report components. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}